{"tid":1542270,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［真相大白 x 點錯數］網傳太子站10傷者中3人「消失」　消防處：第二次點算確認7人送院 (21:45)","createTime":"2019-09-04T20:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T15:23:21.000Z","uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b88831bfbf5a07a295ed63cfa85e4e87cdaea870","tid":1542270,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:28:28.000Z","msg":"網上流傳8月31日衝突中，港鐵太子站<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>共有10名傷者</strong></span>，而消防處當晚<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>僅運送7名傷者至兩間醫院</strong></span>，3名重傷者不知所蹤，流傳有死者被送往廣華醫院殮房，又稱有屍體被抛出公海等。消防處今日（4日）回覆《明報》查詢時表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當晚初步點算有10名傷者，其後再次點算確認7人需送院</strong></span>，或因傷者曾換位而重複計算，或指揮官再次確認人數時有傷者表示不需救護服務，導致兩次點算結果不同。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190904/s00001/1567603251439/【逃犯條例-831】網傳太子站10傷者中3人「消失」-消防處-第二次點算確認7人送院\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190904%2Fs00001%2F1567603251439%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-831%E3%80%91%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%9910%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E4%B8%AD3%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8C%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E3%80%8D-%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%99%95-%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E9%BB%9E%E7%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D7%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6rufjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=8153d6f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190904%2Fs00001%2F1567603251439%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-831%E3%80%91%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%9910%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E4%B8%AD3%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8C%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E3%80%8D-%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%99%95-%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E9%BB%9E%E7%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D7%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2&h=9c5de56f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190904/s00001/1567603251439/【逃犯條例-831】網傳太子站10傷者中3人「消失」-消防處-第二次點算確認7人送院</a>"},{"pid":"e5b3050977330cb108a9d2f0451440d049b64a85","tid":1542270,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:30:48.000Z","msg":"真，唔信？"},{"pid":"52c32034ba67568b32b5ea51d45bf0e7ef91111a","tid":1542270,"uid":36158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:32:11.000Z","msg":"唔相信"},{"pid":"6fcf37879a3d536a76db042ca393213663e82aeb","tid":1542270,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:32:21.000Z","msg":"點錯數?<br />\n屌你當我地傻嫁"},{"pid":"89775352251f02842c586a00b38d1e454e3b64ab","tid":1542270,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:33:24.000Z","msg":"幼稚園都唔會咁樣計錯數啦"},{"pid":"85267284b90201f60abb889c819d7bb8041a212b","tid":1542270,"uid":295304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:41:21.000Z","msg":"其實死者如果係喺醫院以外嘅地方死，<br />\n遺體係會直接送去公眾殮房，<br />\n而喺醫院死先會送去醫院殮房，<br />\n所以如果831太子當場有人死，<br />\n喺醫院殮房冇可能會搵到當場被打死嘅人嘅遺體！<br />\n<br />\n有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"86a0015de5c94d8d9bf7f2d8ff2c95d058aceeb7","tid":1542270,"uid":173323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:43:02.000Z","msg":"毅進仔識由一數到七，未學到十"},{"pid":"cda52ee1d72def3e64f497401f0b446db0092c04","tid":1542270,"uid":316945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:58:12.000Z","msg":"咁膠嘅理由想呃邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係有咁單純做咩唔肯一早攞cctv出嚟正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07a8ca3c65b1d49f2c9a04bab55696692ce2828","tid":1542270,"uid":310805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T21:37:10.000Z","msg":"唔信"},{"pid":"ee299df592d3faa473a43ed13d69b7a10d31cf21","tid":1542270,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T21:50:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eeb4747ac31f47238cf3ad2b14cfe22d05174767","tid":1542270,"uid":315519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T21:55:18.000Z","msg":"七萬個同十萬個就話有得數錯啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1586d91ee517bb3bd842df73efd7e086ba9682a","tid":1542270,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:19:37.000Z","msg":"咁都數錯？于蘭節？"},{"pid":"a3c04cdf111cec4ada1cde7531e8ae7d9d61d249","tid":1542270,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:30:43.000Z","msg":"個位數都可以數錯?"},{"pid":"bc7256e607766dc96f0b793bcd4bd6cfd40b1440","tid":1542270,"uid":306002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:10:08.000Z","msg":"唔信"},{"pid":"2eb1e277d93d8601729758b56024525e748cac81","tid":1542270,"uid":309945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:22:10.000Z","msg":"屌，公開cctv大家幫手一齊數咪知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b596eca6c1bbb11687c1f5e0d0507bcf12d365a","tid":1542270,"uid":277345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:44:56.000Z","msg":"數錯3個，30%喎，一萬個數漏3個就信啫<br />\n仲要重傷可以自行離去？"},{"pid":"2e1126a22117f239e932a69fc7b8c5b52c732fda","tid":1542270,"uid":127121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:23:21.000Z","msg":"西貢少女死亡<br />\n有人話點解咁多處理屍體方法 <br />\n例如：掉落海、扮係跳樓掉條屍落都唔用呢Ｄ方法<br />\n因為個女仔可能真係智障，唔會飲酒跌落海，唔會有情緒失控跳樓，呢兩點都呃唔到佢父母<br />\n所以唯有拎條屍返屋企 <br />\n如果一男一女就係替死鬼或者擺低條屍時佢父母回家<br />\n佢父母一返屋企，就見到一男一女，同埋個女條屍 <br />\n跟住唔肯定邊個報警，或者可能冇報警 因為差佬已經喺附近，之後就即刻入屋拉佢哋<br />\n目的為左滅聲<br />\n個女人未必告得入，因為個男人可能會攬曬罪名，就算告都入都一定判得好輕<br />\n而家吹嘅風話個男人係神打<br />\n目的係為左判誤殺，因為誤殺最多坐三年<br />\n謀殺就會終身<br />\n而佢父母就會做到畏罪自殺，或者係傻咗 入小欖精神病院( 當然係畀人殺死，或者係畀人打到傻咗喇) <br />\n目的只係為咗滅聲"}]}